    Method and Description
    org.springframework.credhub.core.credential.CredHubCredentialOperations.getAllPaths()

    org.springframework.credhub.core.credential.CredHubCredentialTemplate.getAllPaths()
    org.springframework.credhub.support.CredHubRequest.isOverwrite()
    as of CredHub 1.6, use CredHubRequest.mode
    org.springframework.credhub.support.CredHubRequest.CredHubRequestBuilder.overwrite(boolean)
    as of CredHub 1.6, use CredHubRequest.CredHubRequestBuilder.mode(WriteMode)
    org.springframework.credhub.support.CredHubRequest.CredHubRequestBuilder.permission(Permission)
    as of CredHub 2.0, use CredHubPermissionOperations to assign permissions to a credential after it is created
    org.springframework.credhub.support.CredHubRequest.CredHubRequestBuilder.permissions(Collection<? extends Permission>)
    as of CredHub 2.0, use CredHubPermissionOperations to assign permissions to a credential after it is created

    as of CredHub 2.0, use CredHubPermissionOperations to assign permissions to a credential after it is created
